videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Maxx Crosby's 14-yard fumble recovery for a touchdown puts the Eagles up 7-0 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Crosby's scoop-and-score EMU early

videos.description: Alex Briones interception of Eastern Michigan's QB Brogan Roback sets up the Chippewas in the redzone.
videos.headline: CMU's Briones answers with INT

videos.description: Shane Morris guns it deep to Mark Chapman for a 43 yard pass play to set up t he Chippewas deep in Eastern Michigan territory.
videos.headline: Morris finds Chapman for 43-yard gain

videos.description: Shane Morris finds Tyler Conklin for a 4-yard touchdown and ties the game 7-7 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Morris hits Conklin for TD to tie CMU

videos.description: Shane Morris hits Corey Willis deep for a 34 yard gain to put Central Michigan deep in Eastern Michigan territory.
videos.headline: Morris finds Willis for a 34-yard gain

videos.description: Shane Morris hits Corey Willis for a 12-yard touchdown to extend the margin for the Chippewas.
videos.headline: Morris to Willis extends the lead for Central Michigan

videos.description: Brogan Roback's pass is interncepted by Sean Bunting to stop the Eagles drive.
videos.headline: Bunting's INT stops the Eastern Michigan drive

videos.description: Shane Morris finds Jonathan Ward for a 27-yard gain to put Central Michigan in the red zone.
videos.headline: Morris hits Ward for a 27-yard gain

videos.description: Shane Morris hits Corey Willis on a 4-yard shovel pass for a touchdown to push the lead to 28-10 late in the first half.
videos.headline: Morris's third TD pass widens the margin

videos.description: Shaq Vann gallops from 22 yards out for a touchdown to narrow the margin for the Eagles.
videos.headline: Vann races for a TD for Eastern Michigan

videos.description: Josh Cox's 47-yard interception return off Eastern Michigan's Brogan Roback sets up the Chippewas first-and-goal.
videos.headline: Cox's INT and return puts Central Michigan in scoring position

videos.description: Jonathan Ward scores from 3 yards out to add to the lead for the Chippewas.
videos.headline: Ward's second TD widens the gap for Central Michigan

videos.description: Central Michigan's Amari Coleman blast Eastern Michigan's Antoine Porter for a 3-yard loss.
videos.headline: Coleman drops Porter with a big hit

videos.description: John Niupalau's dives for 29-yard touchdown catch to narrow the lead to 35-24 midway through the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Niupalau shows great ball skills for TD catch for Eastern Michigan

videos.description: Brogan Roback hits Mathew Sexton for an 18-yard touchdown to set school record for career touchdown passes with 54. The touchdown cuts the deficit to 35-30 midway through the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: EMU's Roback breaks school record for passing TDs

videos.description: Amari Coleman's second interception results in a 33-yard return for a touchdown to put the game out of reach late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Coleman's pick six seals the deal for Central Michigan
